value: Breeds on the Arctic coast of eastern Siberia (summer specimens known from Cape Baranov) and the Chukchi Peninsula; known to breed on St. Lawrence Island, and from northern and western Alaska, Melville and Baffin Islands south to the southern mainland of Alaska, southern Mackenzie and Hudson Bay. Winters from CaUfornia and Texas south to northern Lower California and central Mexico.
